metadata.name: Not Not Vested
metadata.description:
Experience a moment in web3 history with this meme NFT. It depicts a disagreement among a group of web3 personas who were mistakenly considered as investors in Flux by one of the project's founders. 

Witness the open forum discussion between some of these personas and the Flux founder through the AMA hosted by @ryancarson on Twitter (https://twitter.com/ryancarson/status/1621810906878427137). 

This pieces mint price harnesses the minimum value to invest in Flux, by reversing its significant digits. 

Please note that this piece is for historical reference only and does not represent financial advice or the opinions of the artist.
